The Green Howards Alexandra, Princess of Wales' Own Yorkshire Regiment.|En mémoire de ceux qui sont tombés le 6 juin 1944|In memory of the fallen of June 6th 1944...

En mémoire des soldats des 4th/7th Royal Dragoon Guards tués le 6 juin 1944...
3210 Servicing Commando R.A.F. June 6-15 1944

Sur l'aérodrome de Bazenville le 15 juin 1944, Pierre Clostermann, héros des forces aériennes françaises libres atterrit pour la première fois en France libérée

In memory of the officers and men of The (Notts) Sherwood Rangers Yeomanry who died landing on this beach just before H-Hour on D-Day 6th June 1944 attacking in D.D. swimming tanks they were some of the first British troops ashore...
